data.description: Located in the Burns Brentwood area only blocks away from Harvey Park, this 2 bedroom, 1 bath home home features a living room plus a family room, both with plenty of natural light, a spacious kitchen and a large back yard. Only minutes from parks, schools, shopping and easy access to highways for commuting.
